1. Core Content Pillars

Payments & Strategy (Blue Core): Demystifying money movement. Focuses on regional regulations (PSD3/PSR), regional infrastructures (SEPA, SIC), global standards (ISO 8583, ISO 20022), and emerging instruments (Wero, BaaS, Account-to-Account).

Engineering & AI (Green Core): The builder’s perspective. Architectural breakdowns of high-throughput payment gateways, CI/CD pipelines, and practical implementation of AI Agents for real-time fraud mitigation and reconciliation.

Motivational & Resilience (Yellow Core): Career strategy, navigating organizational complexity in highly regulated environments, and cultivating an industry-first mindset.

2. Professional Distribution Playbook

| Day | Target Time (CET) | Format | Strategic Objective |
| Tuesday | 10:00 AM – 11:00 AM | Technical Carousel | Deep-dive architectural or compliance breakdowns. Tailored for senior tech professionals reviewing technical strategies post-morning stand-ups. |
| Friday | 09:00 AM – 11:00 AM | Editorial Summary | Concise synthesis of weekly long-form posts. Capitalizes on early Friday morning industry reading cycles before weekend log-offs. |

